Record Profile
  Has Name as String
  Has Visits as Int

Make Guest be New Profile with Name be "Ada" and Visits be 1
Change Visits of Guest to Visits of Guest plus 1
Say "{Name of Guest} visited {Visits of Guest} times"

Make Maybe Label be nothing as Maybe String
Change Maybe Label to "returning"
Match Maybe Label
  When Some Label
    Say Label
  When nothing
    Say "new"
